snippet.title: Valdis Story Abyssal City Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
For over forty years, humanity has struggled to survive in the middle of a conflict between gods. Fight your way through the fallen city of Sitheil, and discover the truth behind the goddess war.

Try the demo now at http://tinyurl.com/msy97kp
